{
  "stem": "471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to look at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My very good friend Denik Fuchs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His name was Denik Fuchs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I don't know from where to start first.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "To tell-- to give you an example.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe I-- maybe I can think of it so I can put together one-- one sentence so I'll be able to-- to-- to show you, to prove it to you what kind of man he could be.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, just the word, Goth is coming or he will go by-- you're-- you're-- the death went over you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You feel-- you felt already dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You just-- you were just waiting because you didn't know from where he was going to come.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what I'm trying to say, you can't-- you can't put everything on the paper, you want to write a story, right?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from the story, if you want to make a picture and put them on the screen, impossible to put everything on the screen that occurred.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I've got to give credit to Spielberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] With using a little bit of intelligence, he put the best he could.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and I'm sure, if he will put a little bit more, people wouldn't go and see it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That kind of [INAUDIBLE] will be too much, they-- especially the young people, they will not see it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You see, because he could put more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could put much more, speaking about Goth only.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] So.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stehbunker.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know a stehbunker?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That little box-- I don't know what it's about, about-- about two feet by two feet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were standing 72 hours, you couldn't move till you were lucky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
